A '''garden''' in a [[player-owned house]] is one of the only two types of rooms a player can build starting at level 1 [[Construction]]. Since every house is required to have an exit portal, every player has to have at least one garden or [[formal garden]] in their house. Building a garden costs {{Coins|1000}}.

There are 8 [[hotspot]]s available:
*[[Big Plant space 1]]
*[[Big Plant space 2]]
*[[Big Tree space]]
*[[Centrepiece space]]
*[[Small Plant space 1]]
*[[Small Plant space 2]]
*[[Tree space]]
*[[Tip jar space]]

